I appreciate your uploading this ISO.  I am an IT consultant running a legitimate business in the US.  I service small businesses and more times than not an application has to be re-installed and the business owner has no idea where the original media is located.  I don't even ask any more for the most part.  Although all of the QuickBooks products are available in their entirety at: http://support.quickbooks.intuit.com/support/articles/INF12417 , having access to un-cracked original disc ISOs has been invaluable.  On a side note, if you run a business or support a business, financial software is the last place that you want to have illegitimate software.  Although everything that I've gotten from the Bay has been free of malware (afaik), I couldn't imagine a worse situation than a customer's sensitive financial data being copied out a back-door.  Thank you uploaders.
